dct_title_s: Chapman's sectional map of the surveyed part of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:630,000. Cover title: Chapman's sectional map of Minnesota. Shows county boundaries as of 1867. Publisher's advertising on back cover. Hand colored. Dimensions: 82 x 72 centimeters
